26gt;\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e,","      \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u0026lt;/td\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/tr\u0026gt;\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e,","      \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u0026lt;tr\u0026gt;\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e,","      \u0026quot;\u0026lt;td colspan=\\\u0026quot;9\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;The launch was Boeing\u0026#39;s first conjoined launch of a \u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026quot;/wiki/Boeing_702\\\u0026quot; title=\\\u0026quot;Boeing 702\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;lighter-weight dual-commsat stack\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt; that was specifically designed to take advantage of the \u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026quot;/wiki/Space_launch_market_competition\\\u0026quot; title=\\\u0026quot;Space launch market competition\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;lower-cost\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt; SpaceX Falcon 9 launch vehicle.\u0026lt;sup class=\\\u0026quot;reference\\\u0026quot; id=\\\u0026quot;cite_ref-aw20140310_85-0\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026quot;#cite_note-aw20140310-85\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;span class=\\\u0026quot;cite-bracket\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;[\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;78\u0026lt;span class=\\\u0026quot;cite-bracket\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;]\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/sup\u0026gt;\u0026lt;sup class=\\\u0026quot;reference\\\u0026quot; id=\\\u0026quot;cite_ref-boeing20141112_86-0\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026quot;#cite_note-boeing20141112-86\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;span class=\\\u0026quot;cite-bracket\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;[\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;79\u0026lt;span class=\\\u0026quot;cite-bracket\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;]\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/sup\u0026gt; Per satellite, launch costs were less than US$30 million.\u0026lt;sup class=\\\u0026quot;reference\\\u0026quot; id=\\\u0026quot;cite_ref-sfn20150302_87-0\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026quot;#cite_note-sfn20150302-87\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;span class=\\\u0026quot;cite-bracket\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;[\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;80\u0026lt;span class=\\\u0026quot;cite-bracket\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;]\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/sup\u0026gt; The ABS satellite reached its final destination ahead of schedule and started operations on 10 September 2015.\u0026lt;sup class=\\\u0026quot;reference\\\u0026quot; id=\\\u0026quot;cite_ref-boeing_88-0\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026quot;#cite_note-boeing-88\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;span class=\\\u0026quot;cite-bracket\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;[\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;81\u0026lt;span class=\\\u0026quot;cite-bracket\\\u0026quot;\u0026gt;]\u0026lt;/span\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/a\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/sup\u0026gt;\\n\u0026quot;,","      \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u0026lt;/td\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/tr\u0026gt;\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e,","      \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u0026lt;tr\u0026gt;\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e,","      \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u0026lt;th rowspan=\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e2\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e scope=\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003erow\u003cspan class=\"pl-cce\"\u003e\\\u0026quot;\u003c/span